André Onana Onana (ka amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke abụọ n'ọnwa Eprel n'afọ 1996) bụ onye Cameroon na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agbara ndị otu mba Cameroon bọọlụ.

A mụrụ ya na Nkol Ngok, Onana sonyeere Barcelona na 2010, mgbe ọ malitere na Samuel Eto'o Foundation. Na mbido Jenụwarị 2015, a mara ọkwa na ọ ga-esonyere klọb Ajax nke Dutch na Julaị 2015. E wetara mbugharị ahụ mgbe ọnwa ahụ gasịrị. O mere nke mbụ ya na Jong Ajax na Eerste Divisie na Febụwarị 2015

Ọ bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta ọhụrụ na Ajax na Mee 2017, na-agba ọsọ ruo 2021. Na Machị 2019 ọ bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta ọhụrụ ọzọ, ruo June 2022. N'ọnwa Nọvemba afọ 2019, o kwuru na ya nwere mmasị igwu egwu na Premier League na England.
Na Febụwarị 2021, UEFA machibidoro Onana igwu egwu ruo ọnwa iri na abụọ mgbe ọ nwalere Furosemide, ọgwụ a machibidoro iwu
Ajax kwuru na ọ ṅụrụ ọgwụ nwunye ya n'ụzọ na-ezighị ezi nakwa na ha ga-ekpe ikpe ahụ. Ụlọ ikpe na-ahụ maka egwuregwu belatara mmachibido iwu ahụ ruo ọnwa itoolu na June.
Na ọnwa Jenụwarị 2022 e jikọtara ya na mbugharị na klọb Inter Milan nke Italy. Na Mee 2022 ọ mara ọkwa na ọ na-ahapụ Ajax.
Onana bụbu onye ntorobịa mba Cameroon. A kpọrọ ya aha na ndị otu Cameroon maka egwuregwu enyi na enyi megide France na Mee 2016.
Onana bidoro maka Cameroon na mmeri enyi na enyi 2–1 megide Gabon na Septemba 2016
O gosipụtara na 2021 Africa Cup of Nations egwuregwu nke atọ megide Burkina Faso.
Nwa nwanne nna ya, Fabrice Ondoa, na-agbakwa bọọlụ dị ka onye nche.
Na Mee 2019, Onana kwuru okwu banyere ịbụ onye nche ojii, na-ekwu na ha aghaghị ịrụsi ọrụ ike karịa ndị ọcha ibe ha n'ihi echiche na-ezighị ezi banyere ha na-eme "mmehie".
